# Installation
> `npm install --save @types/p5`

# Summary
This package contains type definitions for p5 (https://github.com/processing/p5.js).

# Details
Files were exported from https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/master/types/p5.

### Additional Details

 * Dependencies: none
 * Global values: none
